  meta_action_code STRING OPTIONS(description='The \'meta_action_code\' field indicates the type of action performed on the FHIR resource, such as creation, update, or deletion. It is vital for audit trails and tracking changes within healthcare systems, ensuring transparency and accountability in data management. This field helps in understanding the lifecycle of a resource and is crucial for maintaining accurate and up-to-date patient records.'),
  hl7_v2_source_interface STRING OPTIONS(description='The \'hl7_v2_source_interface\' field identifies the source interface from which the HL7 v2 message originated. It is important for interoperability and data exchange between different healthcare systems, ensuring that data is accurately transmitted and received. This field helps in tracing the origin of data and is crucial for troubleshooting and maintaining data integrity across systems.'),
