  patient_class_code STRING OPTIONS(description='The \"patient_class_code\" field identifies the category of the patient during the encounter, such as inpatient, outpatient, or emergency. It is used for classifying the type of care provided and affects billing, resource allocation, and care planning. This classification is crucial for understanding the context of the encounter and ensuring appropriate care delivery.'),
